title: The Swift Programming Language
description:
Swift is a new programming language for creating iOS and OS X apps. Swift builds on the best of C and Objective-C, without the constraints of C compatibility. Swift adopts safe programming patterns and adds modern features to make programming easier, more flexible, and more fun. - A detailed guide delving into each language feature.
- A formal reference for the language.
